{
  "stem": "11723.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I guess the people who looted the place did not realize that Meissen china was valuable, so it was still there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my grandmother was a very fancy lady in her salamander shoes by the bags full [LAUGHS] were there, and fancy hats, and evening gowns.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I had a great time as a kid putting them on, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyway, we moved into that place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I said, in 1948, my brother was born.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were already living there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And now in 1948, they nationalized the store.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So now, my father had no means of making a living.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Plus, if you did not hold onto-- if you did not have a job, you were-- how can I translate that?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was punishable by prison if you were a loiterer or I don't know-- whatever you would call somebody who doesn't have a job.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never mind that you didn't-- you weren't on public assistance, which nobody was on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But even if you lived off of your own money, it doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was punishable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a punishable crime, punishable by prison if you didn't work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there's my father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They take his livelihood away, and now they were going to throw in prison because he doesn't have a job.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he went to the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Jewish congregation, and they gave him a job in the [NON-ENGLISH] it was called.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he would be going around to the countryside, all around the countryside, collecting dues from the different villages where some people went and resettled.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's what he did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meantime of course, that's not what we lived on, but whatever was left from the business, whatever they could salvage from it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the-- this-- this was in 1948.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
